      },
      "index": 0,
      "text": "As you heard, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHouseKarosas],House Karosas]] has suffered greatly at the hands of the Directorate. We can't change that, but we can show Lord Karosas that we're his allies, and that our word can be trusted.\n\nWe need his help with our data archive, yes. But that isn't why I agreed to this mission. If we are to prevail against the Directorate, I <i>must</i> unite the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreFoundingHouses],Founding Houses]] under the Restoration's banner. Without their support, we'll have no way of replacing our losses.",
