    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c8343ebefafcbef77056953"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "She's called the <i>Newgrange</i>. She's a transport vessel, ostensibly civilian, named for an old line of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreYardship],Yardships]].\n\nThe <i>Newgrange</i> has been certified for commercial flight in the Directorate, the [[DM.Factions[faction_Liao],Capellan Confederation]], and the [[DM.Factions[faction_TaurianConcordat],Taurian Concordat]]. In all other ways, she's completely unremarkable… at least, that's what her official paperwork says.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "I gather that Lord Karosas disagrees with the official paperwork.",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c2e8da94653fab74a73ee16"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        },
        {
          "responseText": "Uh-huh. And what's the real story?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 19,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c46b182f03fe5db84d9d1c9"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        },
        {
          "responseText": "And what if the official paperwork is right?",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 20,
          "hideIfUnavailable": false,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cc85d7f8deb491d38f72475"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
