    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c4dca65774cebe33b1efaac"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "The Anvelt fueling station was designed for civilian use. It isn't a hardened target, and its components can't withstand a sustained attack.\n\nIf we go in while the <i>Newgrange</i> is refueling and blow the station's primary fuel reservoir, her armor won't count for much. The resulting explosion will smash her like an egg.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
